name: #smolCvnt - Hancock
description: @DolCreative - A smol tribute to, quite possibly, the biggest crook of the crew, deemed to have acted unlawfully, lined his pockets off death & suffering, generally looks like an absolute slime ball. What better way to commemorate the Tories shafting the arts again than immortalising them in smol art? He certainly didn't fix me up with one of his special contracts for this piece - Hancock. 10x10 pixel pop art inspired portrait.
